name: Fishing Impossible
description:
Fishing Impossible: Fishing Impossible is a cool Boat Control game , but not as you know! You are the controller to make Fishing possible, Direct boats into Fishing spots and make them fishing and direct them off the screen ,Avoid boast crashing into each other, Be careful with cyclones!



Fishing impossible has high resolution graphics and effects for iPhone and iPad Retina display.



FEATURES:

-Eight levels: paradise bay, seahorse peninsula, sunset archipelago, strait of cancoon, autumm atoll, starfish island, frozen cove, larry's lagoon

-cool water effects

-cute hand painted art

Follow us on Twitter @FishImpossible
